opening large stores would hurt small shop owners 
the 50000member association of small retailers vowed to do 
our best to prevent the decisions from being enforced 
us negotiators viewed shortening of the time for opening large 
stores as a major victory because it would open the way for large 
american and other foreign retailers to set up operations one of 
the beneficiaries is expected to be the toys r us chain 
