a 37year fight to desegregate schools in 
impoverished st helena parish supposedly ended last year when 
blacks and whites began attending classes under the same roof 
but when white school board members fired the black 
superintendent it showed the fight was far from over 
the firing which apparently was decided at a closed meeting and 
