telescope dozens of times and is prepared for just about anything 
that might go wrong 
im confident we can do it under almost any circumstance he 
said nasas real good at whatifs and weve done a lot 
whatifs what if this part doesnt work what if the arm fails 
completely 
mission specialists bruce mccandless ii and kathryn sullivan 
veteran spacewalkers will go out to help remove or fix the 
telescope if necessary 
