ryans sister andrea says boy i wish it would be me that could 
stay home but this is what ryan wants to do and i want what he 
wants 
mrs white moved her family to cicero about 20 miles from their 
home saying they did not want to stay where they were unwanted 
white said at the time that he did not want to die in kokomo or to 
be buried there they were welcomed by the new community and the 
school system 
