company officials said two fires broke out on separate decks 
within 15 minutes crew members reportedly extinguished the first 
fire then discovered a bigger blaze one deck below 
scandinavian news reports quoted survivors as saying the fire 
began on a low deck beneath the ferrys water line and near the 
stern thick smoke spread upward through the deck where 
passengers cars were parked and through a higher deck where a 
casino and bars are located 
